‣ JPG #1 (in 2:3 ratio) prints: 4"x6", 6"x9", 8"x12", 10"x15", 12"x18", 16"x24", 20"x30"

‣ Once your payment has been processed, you will receive an email from Etsy letting you know that your files are available for download. Simply click on the link in the email to download your files. Your files will also be available here: https://www.etsy.com/your/purchases.
‣ Once downloaded, you can save the files to your computer; simply print and frame!
